## 3. Chuẩn Code & Quy Tắc Đặt Tên

### 3.1 Đặt Tên File

| Loại | Pattern | Ví dụ |
|------|---------|-------|
| Module | `<feature>.module.ts` | [telegram.module.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.module.ts), [chat-hub.module.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.module.ts) |
| Service | `<feature>.service.ts` hoặc `<feature>-<sub>.service.ts` | [telegram.service.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.service.ts), [livechat-api.service.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/livechat-api.service.ts) |
| Controller | `<feature>.controller.ts` hoặc `<feature>-<role>.controller.ts` | [chat-hub.controller.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.controller.ts), [livechat-management.controller.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/livechat-management.controller.ts) |
| Adapter | `<platform>.adapter.ts` | [telegram.adapter.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.adapter.ts), [livechat.adapter.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/livechat.adapter.ts) |
| Handler | `<platform>-webhook.handler.ts` | [telegram-webhook.handler.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram-webhook.handler.ts) |
| DTO | `<feature>.dto.ts` | [livechat.dto.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/dto/livechat.dto.ts), [send-message.dto.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/dto/send-message.dto.ts) |
| Interface | `<concept>.interface.ts` | [standard-message.interface.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/common/interfaces/standard-message.interface.ts), [api-response.interface.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/common/interfaces/api-response.interface.ts) |
| Types | `<feature>.types.ts` | [telegram.types.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.types.ts), [livechat-api.types.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/livechat-api.types.ts) |
| Constants | `<feature>.constants.ts` | [livechat.constants.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/common/constants/livechat.constants.ts) |
| Enum file | [index.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/common/enums/index.ts) (barrel export) | [common/enums/index.ts](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/common/enums/index.ts) |

### 3.2 Đặt Tên Class & Interface

| Loại | Pattern | Ví dụ |
|------|---------|-------|
| Module | `<Feature>Module` | [TelegramModule](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.module.ts#11-30), [ChatHubModule](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.module.ts#5-12) |
| Service | `<Feature>Service` | [ChatHubService](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.service.ts#11-127), [LivechatApiService](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/livechat-api.service.ts#15-371) |
| Controller | `<Feature>Controller` | [ChatHubController](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.controller.ts#7-54), [WebhookGatewayController](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/webhook/webhook-gateway.controller.ts#19-93) |
| Adapter | `<Platform>Adapter` | [TelegramAdapter](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.adapter.ts#24-325), [LivechatAdapter](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/livechat.adapter.ts#16-214) |
| Handler | `<Platform>WebhookHandler` | [TelegramWebhookHandler](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram-webhook.handler.ts#14-73) |
| Gateway | `<Feature>Gateway` | [AgentGateway](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/agent-gateway/agent.gateway.ts#21-194) |
| DTO | `<Action><Feature>Dto` | [SendMessageDto](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/dto/send-message.dto.ts#5-53), [RegisterWebhookDto](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/dto/livechat.dto.ts#153-184) |
| Interface | `I<Concept>` | [IChatAdapter](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/common/interfaces/standard-message.interface.ts#30-42), [IStandardMessage](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/common/interfaces/standard-message.interface.ts#11-24), [IWebhookHandler](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/common/interfaces/standard-message.interface.ts#78-93) |
| Enum | `PascalCase` (giá trị SCREAMING_SNAKE) | `Platform.TELEGRAM`, `SenderType.AGENT` |
| Type | `<Feature><Concept>` | [TelegramChatType](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.types.ts#66-67), [AgentRoutingStatus](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/livechat-api.types.ts#24-28) |

### 3.3 Đặt Tên Biến & Method

| Loại | Pattern | Ví dụ |
|------|---------|-------|
| Private field | `private readonly <name>` | `private readonly logger`, `private readonly handlers` |
| Logger | `new Logger(<ClassName>.name)` | `new Logger(ChatHubService.name)` |
| Map/Registry | `Map<Key, Value>` | `Map<Platform, IChatAdapter>` |
| Handler method | `handle<Event>()` | [handleIncomingMessage()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.service.ts#47-69), [handleWebhook()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/livechat/livechat-webhook.handler.ts#31-80) |
| Parse method | `parse<Type>Message()` | [parseTextMessage()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.adapter.ts#198-213), [parsePhotoMessage()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/adapters/telegram/telegram.adapter.ts#214-237) |
| Register method | `register<What>()` | [registerAdapter()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.service.ts#19-23), [registerNotifier()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.service.ts#36-44) |
| Getter | `get<What>()` | [getHandler()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/webhook/webhook-registry.service.ts#27-42), [getRegisteredPlatforms()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/webhook/webhook-registry.service.ts#50-56) |
| Check method | `has<What>()` | [hasHandler()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/webhook/webhook-registry.service.ts#43-49) |
| Route method | `routeTo<Target>()` | [routeToCustomer()](file:///d:/The%20Black%20Ants/CSC/CSC-Adapter/src/modules/chat-hub/chat-hub.service.ts#72-101) |

### 3.4 Cấu Trúc Thư Mục

```
src/
├── main.ts                          ← Entry point
├── app.module.ts                    ← Root module
├── common/                          ← Shared (interfaces, enums, constants)
│   ├── enums/
│   ├── interfaces/
│   ├── constants/
│   ├── guards/         (TODO)       ← Auth guards
│   ├── filters/        (TODO)       ← Exception filters
│   ├── interceptors/   (TODO)       ← Response transform
│   └── decorators/     (TODO)       ← Custom decorators
└── modules/
    ├── chat-hub/                    ← Core Hub
    ├── webhook/                     ← Webhook Gateway
    ├── agent-gateway/               ← WebSocket cho Agent
    └── adapters/
        ├── telegram/                ← Telegram adapter
        └── livechat/                ← LiveChat adapter
```

